*GeoRuby-2.5.2 (04 Apr 2015)

  04 Apr 2015; Hans de Graaff <graaff@gentoo.org> +GeoRuby-2.5.2.ebuild:
  Version bump. Add ruby22.

  13 Mar 2015; Manuel Rüger <mrueg@gentoo.org> -GeoRuby-2.2.1-r1.ebuild:
  Remove old.

  13 Mar 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> GeoRuby-2.2.1-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for x86, wrt bug #542994

  12 Mar 2015; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> GeoRuby-2.2.1-r2.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #542994

  08 Feb 2015;  <hanno@gentoo.org> metadata.xml:
  remove myself as maintainer, goes to sci-geosciences and ruby herd

*GeoRuby-2.2.1-r3 (01 Aug 2014)

